<div class="riskr-testimonials">
  <div class="riskr-testimonials__inner page-width">

    <div class="riskr-testimonials__header">
      <span class="riskr-testimonials__label">Social Proof</span>
      <h2 class="riskr-testimonials__headline">
        Trusted by professionals<br>who take themselves seriously.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-testimonials__grid">

      <div class="riskr-testimonials__card">
        <p class="riskr-testimonials__quote">"I wore this shirt to our Q3 all-hands. Three people asked where I got it. I said I couldn't disclose that at this time."</p>
        <div class="riskr-testimonials__author">
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__name">T. Morrison</span>
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__role">Chief People Officer, Series B Startup</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="riskr-testimonials__card">
        <p class="riskr-testimonials__quote">"This garment has done more for my personal brand than 18 months of LinkedIn content. I've been promoted twice since wearing it. Correlation is not causation. But."</p>
        <div class="riskr-testimonials__author">
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__name">D. Harrington</span>
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__role">VP of Strategic Everything, Fortune 500</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="riskr-testimonials__card">
        <p class="riskr-testimonials__quote">"I ordered one for myself and four for my direct reports. Team alignment has never been higher. Our NPS is up 12 points. I'm not saying it's the shirts."</p>
        <div class="riskr-testimonials__author">
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__name">R. Patel</span>
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__role">Director of Alignment, Management Consulting</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="riskr-testimonials__card">
        <p class="riskr-testimonials__quote">"Honestly, I don't even work in an office. I work from home. But I wear this shirt on Zoom calls and people respond to me differently. There's a before and an after."</p>
        <div class="riskr-testimonials__author">
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__name">K. Osei</span>
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__role">Head of Remote Synergy, Fully Distributed</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="riskr-testimonials__card">
        <p class="riskr-testimonials__quote">"I gave one to my manager as a gift. She now reports to me. I am not legally allowed to say more."</p>
        <div class="riskr-testimonials__author">
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__name">J. Blackwell</span>
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__role">Newly Promoted, Mid-Market SaaS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="riskr-testimonials__card">
        <p class="riskr-testimonials__quote">"Five stars. Comfortable. Well-made. The text on the front accurately describes my professional aspirations. Washed well. Would operationalize again."</p>
        <div class="riskr-testimonials__author">
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__name">A. Chen</span>
          <span class="riskr-testimonials__role">Senior Individual Contributor</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .riskr-testimonials {
    background: #f7f7f7;
    padding-block: 96px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 0 80px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    padding-top: 10px;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__card {
    padding: 40px;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    margin: -1px 0 0 -1px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 28px;
    background: #fff;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__card:hover {
    background: #fafafa;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.72);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__author {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__name {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .riskr-testimonials__role {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .riskr-testimonials__card:nth-child(2).riskr-reveal { transition-delay: 0.07s; }
    .riskr-testimonials__card:nth-child(3).riskr-reveal { transition-delay: 0.14s; }
    .riskr-testimonials__card:nth-child(4).riskr-reveal { transition-delay: 0.07s; }
    .riskr-testimonials__card:nth-child(5).riskr-reveal { transition-delay: 0.14s; }
    .riskr-testimonials__card:nth-child(6).riskr-reveal { transition-delay: 0.21s; }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .riskr-testimonials__header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .riskr-testimonials__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .riskr-testimonials {
      padding-block: 72px;
    }

    .riskr-testimonials__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .riskr-testimonials__card {
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Riskr Testimonials",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "riskr-testimonials-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Riskr Testimonials"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
